  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Las Vegas Cool Hand, known as Cool Hand in Europe, is a casino game developed by Tarantula Studios and published by Take-Two Interactive for the Game Boy Color. It was released on December 1, 1998 in North America and Europe. The game was ported exclusively in Europe on 1998 for the Game Boy.",
